# ============================================================================
# QUICK START GUIDE
# ============================================================================
#
# For Production/Staging API (dev.mtt.cdao.us):
# 1. Get Keycloak credentials from your team
# 2. Uncomment and fill in OPTION 1 variables above
# 3. Restart dev server: npm run dev
# 4. Log in through Keycloak when prompted
# 5. Verify token exists: localStorage.getItem('marketplace_auth_token')
#
# For Local Development with Mock Auth:
# 1. Start local backend: cd .. && docker-compose up backend
# 2. Uncomment OPTION 2 variables above
# 3. Restart dev server: npm run dev
# 4. Mock user will be automatically authenticated
#
# ============================================================================

